    <a class="col"><i class="fas fa-3x fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    <a class="col"><i class="fas fa-5x fa-users"></i><p>Choose and contact the dev</p></a>
    <a class="col"><i class="fas fa-3x fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    <a class="col"><i class="fas fa-5x fa-check"></i><p>Get your done project!</p></a>
  </div>

